merge_multi_port_to_single_port(25.10)  merge_multi_port_to_single_port(25.10)

Name
       merge_multi_port_to_single_port

Syntax
       merge_multi_port_to_single_port {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: false

       When  set to true, multiple ports in a LEF PIN are merged into a single
       port. However, the pin should not have the  MUSTJOINALLPORTS  attribute
       as it specifies that all of the ports must be connected individually.

